{"tid":1927630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"娛樂台公關狗全部入來","createTime":"2020-03-16T01:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T04:41:05.000Z","uid":219225,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f48b5f2b16550d836141233d17f00a0f8e043d56","tid":1927630,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:34:28.000Z","msg":"選戰臨近，公關公司空群而出<br />\n<br />\n熱門不斷被無聊 post 長期佔據<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特此宣佈連登進入緊急狀態，直至選舉完結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所有手足，包括黃絲連登 admin 必須立即採取以下措施，防止連登淪陷<br />\n<br />\n1、凡見熱門有膠 post 淫 post 等與抗爭無關者，一律舉報<br />\n<br />\n2、若有黃絲 admin 發現有會員經常開無聊 post 而上熱門者，請調查其真實身份是否涉及紅色資本所聘請之公關公司，掌握證據後請立即封鎖其帳戶<br />\n<br />\n3、所有手足只推行動及文宣 post , 其他一律推文<br />\n<br />\n4、所有會員自律，唔好開同推無聊 post<br />\n<br />\n事關重大，香港前途就係大家手上<br />\n<br />\n最後：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全民參政 光復議會</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a4c1e528b7f56352e3cd0f95d791eb63024a712","tid":1927630,"uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:35:08.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n樓豬五毛專登分化愚樂台手足"},{"pid":"d838472dabc8a4505d6bdbcac55a830b576f45f5","tid":1927630,"uid":219225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4a4c1e528b7f56352e3cd0f95d791eb63024a712","tid":1927630,"uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:35:08.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n樓豬五毛專登分化愚樂台手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:38:34.000Z","msg":"我已經擇低左你名交比黃絲admin"},{"pid":"13592ed9c11c31a00a0a56e82360cba09cac1657","tid":1927630,"uid":165368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:39:56.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"65c1a76e924a7ccd4829d8fed219ecca2222f8d2","tid":1927630,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:47:54.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"1ddf739fa6a4b501315393bb0f88916ccd68887e","tid":1927630,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"